Metadata.Creator: FactMiners and The Softalk Apple Project
Metadata.Comment: MAGAZINE Ground Truth Storage for softalkv2n08apr1982 of the 48-issue run of Softalk Magazine.

DocumentStructure.Comment: This branch of the MAGAZINE #GTS format provides the metamodel and associated datasets that describe the complex document structure of this ISSUE of a magazine (or other serial publication).

ContentDepiction.Comment: This branch of the MAGAZINE #GTS format provides the metadata model and associated datasets that cover the content depiction model -- the "what this publication is about" -- dimension of the magazine. Note that there is no hard line between the document structure and its content depiction model. In fact, a significant aspect of the MAGAZINE #GTS metamodel is an explicit attempt to address the intersection of the document's structure and its content.

ContentRelationships.Comment: Similiar to the model-composition role of Issuing Rules of the DocumentStructure model, ContentRelationships are specifications of the linkages between entities in the ContentDepiction model, i.e. the edges (and their properties) between ContentDepiction nodes in a graph expression of the model.

Advertisers.Comment: The Companies and Organizations included here are cited as Advertisers in the Advertisers Index. See the Advertisements dataset in the DocumentStructure portion of the MAGAZINE #GTS model for page-specific sightings.

StaffAssignments.Comment: This dataset connects People with the StaffPositions they served for THIS ISSUE of the magazine based on the masthead.
